        <p class="rj-program-card__description">
          A flexible alternative to traditional juvenile justice. Activities are tailored to each situation to interrupt harmful patterns and keep youth out of the justice system.
        </p>
        <ul class="rj-program-card__tags">
          <li>Traditional Teen Court with peer jury</li>
          <li>RJ Circle with family</li>
          <li>Circle with person harmed</li>
          <li>Circle with school</li>
