        <p class="rj-program-card__description">
          Structured, facilitated conversations that bring together those affected by harm. Circles are broader and community-inclusive; conferences are more formal and targeted.
        </p>
        <ul class="rj-program-card__tags">
          <li>Person who caused harm &amp; person harmed</li>
          <li>Community &amp; family support</li>
          <li>Guided by a trained facilitator</li>
